@source_line 30
@purpose Tests if a single-character string is an ASCII letter (a-z, A-Z) or underscore. Underscore is included because identifiers can start with _.
@notes Implemented as an exhaustive OR chain over all 53 characters (26 lower + 26 upper + underscore). [src: lexer.aria:29-40]

