@fn _add_token
@sig (lex: Lexer, kind: TokenKind, text: str, start_line: i64, start_col: i64, start_offset: i64) -> Lexer
@source_file src/lexer/lexer.aria
@source_line 120
@purpose Appends a token to the Lexer's token list. Takes the start position (captured before scanning began) so the token's location points to where it begins in source, not where scanning ended.
@post tokens list grows by one element. All other state preserved.

