@fn _newline
@sig (lex: Lexer) -> Lexer
@source_file src/lexer/lexer.aria
@source_line 200
@purpose Advances past a newline character: increments pos by 1, increments line by 1, resets col to 1.
@pre Current character at pos is \n.
@post pos += 1, line += 1, col = 1. Token list and other state unchanged.

